x}}-{\frac {Z\sigma }{\sqrt {n}}},\quad {\bar {x}}+{\frac {Z\sigma }{\sqrt =
{n}}}\right)}</annotation>
  </semantics>
</math></span><img src=3D"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/rend=
